{"tid":1556824,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"支持良心小店嘅同我入黎再去OpenRice","createTime":"2019-09-10T01:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T01:53:32.000Z","uid":92964,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3d3b3d4da8e27fec31a9244bf6402dcc2005d11d","tid":1556824,"uid":92964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:25:29.000Z","msg":"四喜麵包好多貨 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1554996/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1554996/page/2</a><br />\n睇到上面個個post，覺得香港人真係好勁，入間麵包舖都要大排長龍，真係10間美心都唔夠你地玩啦。不過，大家要知道香港人最叻係咩，係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三分鐘熱度</span></span></strong>啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地要將小店嘅好味道，一傳十十傳百，名留青史，發揚光大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>無錯，我地就係要去OpenRice</strong></span><br />\n連登仔推咗加藤屋幾個月，理鬼你係連登有幾千個正皮，一個普通人搵野食就係去OpenRice，但你望下OpenRice吖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9OZwZs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9OZwZs.png&h=8614fec7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當你見間餐廳咁少舔舔脷，仲要好壞參半，有間仲要係零好評，喂大佬啊，你都唔會想去呢間餐廳食啦係咪啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以所有食過呢D良心小店嘅人，全部同我去OpenRice寫食評，讚下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你連打幾十字Po張相你都覺得麻煩，你連和理非都唔配做啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢樣野無成本又唔會比人秋後算帳架，放心做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地終極目標係要令港豬，甚至係藍絲，都一齊去小店幫襯，等班職員做到無停手，一粒飯一個包都無得留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937b051e8befca2d9bac55f978b53965b2247cc0","tid":1556824,"uid":92964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"41813e8190fbe8ce13fc02fc61d3dbdf857d658b","tid":1556824,"uid":92964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:31:08.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4da7e4c6c510d07ba0a34a9983e2db966702f068","tid":1556824,"uid":92964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:31:20.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"726c2f031089ce2dd663e9420f0ea05c32986408","tid":1556824,"uid":92964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"33ae8e76763187ad882c70cf442ab6bc79800c75","tid":1556824,"uid":176840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"笑咗"},{"pid":"20aabe18da35514a8dee7bd7abf2ff4b706a38dc","tid":1556824,"uid":92964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41cdca3bcc54fcca0118f8077a982e95eff3ece8","tid":1556824,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:43:34.000Z","msg":"咩年代啊重用openrice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007dcf7d1fb50a02b78dcaa7ae6aebadf5566f42","tid":1556824,"uid":24747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"上google評分留comments好過啦，仲用openrice<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0upU5y4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0upU5y4.jpg&h=a74dae1c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}